SCOPE / NOTICE

This MIT license covers the original work in this repository: the explorer
application (`explorer/`), the build tooling (`tools/`), and the documentation
(`docs/`, `MANUAL.md`, etc.).

It does NOT cover, and this repository does NOT distribute:

  * The Williams arcade sound ROMs for Defender (1980), Stargate / Defender II
    (1981), and Robotron 2084 (1982). Those ROM images and their source are
    © Williams Electronics and are not included here. The explorer requires you
    to supply your own copy (from a MAME romset you are licensed to use, dumped
    from hardware you own, or assembled from source you obtain yourself).

  * Third-party tools and dependencies — e.g. the vasm assembler and the npm
    packages in `explorer/package.json` — which remain under their own licenses.
